[['CentralBank.get_latest_monetary_policy', {'name': 'CentralBank.get_latest_monetary_policy', 'description': 'Retrieve the latest monetary policy from the central bank.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'policy', 'description': 'The latest monetary policy.'}]}], ['InfrastructureInvestment.get_latest_data', {'name': 'InfrastructureInvestment.get_latest_data', 'description': 'Get the latest data on infrastructure investment.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'investment_data', 'description': 'The latest infrastructure investment data.'}]}], ['InfrastructureInvestment.analyze_monetary_policy_impact', {'name': 'InfrastructureInvestment.analyze_monetary_policy_impact', 'description': 'Analyze the impact of monetary policy adjustments on infrastructure investment.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'investment_data', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The latest infrastructure investment data.'}, {'name': 'monetary_policy', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The latest monetary policy.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis_result', 'description': 'The analysis result of monetary policy impact on infrastructure investment.'}]}], ['InfrastructureInvestment.compare_investment_changes', {'name': 'InfrastructureInvestment.compare_investment_changes', 'description': 'Compare infrastructure investment changes under different monetary policies.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'previous_policy', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The previous monetary policy.'}, {'name': 'current_policy', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The current monetary policy.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'comparison_result', 'description': 'The comparison result of infrastructure investment changes under different policies.'}]}], ['InfrastructureInvestment.predict_future_investment', {'name': 'InfrastructureInvestment.predict_future_investment', 'description': 'Predict future infrastructure investment based on the analysis.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'analysis_result', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The analysis result of monetary policy impact on infrastructure investment.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'prediction', 'description': 'The prediction of future infrastructure investment.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
